sources.title: Daughter of the Tong (1939) LADY CRIME BOSS
sources.description:
Stars: Evelyn Brent, Grant Withers, Dorothy Short, Dave O'Brien
Director: Raymond K. Johnson

A tough G-man matches wits with a sultry Dragon Lady who poses as a geisha girl by the day and a crime boss by night.
